request.description:
Establish the WebSocket connection. After connecting, use the following JSONs in the Message tab:

1. LOGIN:
{
  "type": "LOGIN",
  "username": "PostmanTester"
}

2. JOIN ROOM:
{
  "type": "JOIN",
  "username": "PostmanTester",
  "roomId": "general"
}

3. MESSAGE:
{
  "type": "CHAT",
  "username": "PostmanTester",
  "roomId": "general",
  "content": "Hello!"
}
